Shadenav

What the project is for
	Bootstrap 3 navbar and dropdown shadow and slide effects animation plugin
		-Works with default, static top and fixed navbars ( See https://getbootstrap.com/docs/3.3/getting-started/#examples-navbars )

How to configure and install it
	Markup
		Note: Include Shadenav CSS and JS in correct order
		1. Wrap nav element with div containing appropriate Shadenav wrapper class
			-.sn-default for (default) navbar
			-.sn-static for static top navbar
			-.sn-fixed for fixed navbar
		2. Add slide effect animation class to "dropdown" element
			-.jq-slide for Jquery slide effect
			-.jqui-slide for JqueryUI slide effect
		3. Wrap "dropdown-menu" element with div
		4. Wrap "dropdown-menu" element's links' text with divs
	JavaScript
		Note: JqueryUI required for JqueryUI slide effect
		5. Add slide effect animation script to your JavaScript

An example of how to use it or get it running
	https://tightcode.github.io/shadenav

